    v2 = wp.exp(0.16)
    v1 = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.40 - tmp + 0.54) / (v1 + 0.54 - v0 + 0.39)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.99 / tmp + 0.87)) / wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.07)))
    v1 = v2
